Description: Semiparametric and parametric estimation of INAR models including a finite sample refinement for the semiparametric setting, different procedures to bootstrap INAR data and flexible simulation of INAR data.
		Faymonville, M., Jentsch, C., Weiß, C.H. and Aleksandrov, B. (2022) "Semiparametric Estimation of INAR Models using Roughness Penalization" <doi:10.1007/s10260-022-00655-0>
		Jentsch, C. and Weiß, C.H. (2017) "Bootstrapping INAR Models" <doi:10.3150/18-BEJ1057>
		Drost, F., Van den Akker, R. and Werker, B. (2009) "Efficient estimation of auto-regression parameters and innovation distributions for semiparametric integer-valued AR(p) models" <doi:10.1111/j.1467-9868.2008.00687.x>
